Affiliation = {Neunzig, C (Corresponding Author), Ruhr Univ Bochum, Chair Prod Syst, Industriestr 38C, D-44894 Bochum, Germany.
   Neunzig, C (Corresponding Author), Bosch Rexroth AG, Bexbacher Str 72, D-66424 Homburg, Germany.
